OL,4,Cbuildings law
OL,6,FLegislation on defective buildings is
OL,7,Fto be introduced to increase the time
OL,8,Flimit for owners to bring compensation
OL,9,Fclaims, Communities Minister Gordon
OL,10,FLyons has said.
OL,12,FMr Lyons announced plans to bring the
OL,13,Flaw in line with England and Wales
OL,14,Ffollowing a controversy around the
OL,15,FVictoria Square apartments in Belfast.
OL,17,FResidents of the city centre complex
OL,18,Fhad to leave their homes in 2019 after
OL,19,Fstructural issues were found.
