OL,6,FHowever, their bid for compensation
OL,7,Fwas struck out in court last month
OL,8,Fbecause in Northern Ireland such
OL,9,Fclaims must be made within six years
OL,10,Fof a building being completed.
OL,12,FAssembly members have faced calls to
OL,13,Fchange the law to extend the statutory
OL,14,Ftime limit to 30 years, the same as in
OL,15,FEngland and Wales.
