OL,6,FMr Lyons told the Assembly: "I intend
OL,7,Fto bring to the Assembly, as a matter
OL,8,Fof urgency, legislation to provide the
OL,9,Fsame protection associated with
OL,10,Fdefective premises for citizens in
OL,11,FNorthern Ireland as afforded elsewhere
OL,12,Fin the UK.
OL,14,F"This proposed Bill will introduce new
OL,15,Fprovisions into the Limitation
OL,16,F(Northern Ireland) Order 1989,
OL,17,Festablishing a retrospective period of
OL,18,Fup to 30 years and a prospective
OL,19,Fperiod of up to 15 years in which a
OL,20,Fparty can take action for defective
OL,21,Fpremises."
