OL,6,FMr Lyons added: "In order for us to
OL,7,Fcontinue to deliver for people here, I
OL,8,Fam seeking the ongoing urgent support
OL,9,Fof my Executive colleagues and this
OL,10,FAssembly to ensure the swift passage
OL,11,Fof this legislation which will provide
OL,12,FNorthern Ireland residents with the
OL,13,Fsame recourse and protections as
OL,14,Fprescribed in other jurisdictions
OL,15,Fwhere a building is shown to be
OL,16,Fdefective.
