OL,6,F"Given the urgency, I am writing to
OL,7,FExecutive colleagues today to seek
OL,8,Ftheir support and approval to
OL,9,Fintroduce new legislation under the
OL,10,FAccelerated Passage process.
OL,12,F"This primary legislation will address
OL,13,Fthe period under which action can be
OL,14,Ftaken with regard to defective
OL,15,Fbuildings and addresses the unfair
OL,16,Fdisparity that currently exists and
OL,17,Fdisadvantages our people."
