OL,6,FMr Lyons said the current disparity in
OL,7,Flaws placed people in Northern Ireland
OL,8,Fat a "clear disadvantage" compared to
OL,9,Fthe rest of the UK.
OL,11,FHe said: "It is clear there is an
OL,12,Furgent need for fit-for-purpose
OL,13,Flegislation which provides improved
OL,14,Fprotection to all those who live in
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland."
