OL,6,FMr Lyons said it was initially
OL,7,F"unclear" which department should take
OL,8,Fon responsibility, but after
OL,9,Fdiscussions with the Agriculture,
OL,10,FEnvironment and Rural Affairs Minister
OL,11,FAndrew Muir last week, the transfer of
OL,12,Ffunctions order has been moved to his
OL,13,Fdepartment.
OL,15,FLast month, it was announced that
OL,16,Fresidents of the Victoria Square
OL,17,Fapartments would be issued with
OL,18,Frefunds for the rates bills they had
OL,19,Fpaid during the period when their
OL,20,Fproperties were uninhabitable.
