OL,6,FTheir legal bid for compensation was
OL,7,Fstruck out in Belfast High Court after
OL,8,Fthe judge ruled it fell outside the
OL,9,Fterms of existing legislation.
OL,11,FThe case had been taken against
OL,12,Farchitects involved in the design and
OL,13,Ftwo building companies. All deny any
OL,14,Fliability.
OL,16,FResidents had to leave their homes in
OL,17,F2019 after a defect was identified in
OL,18,Fa structural column. They had been
OL,19,Funable to return, but were still
OL,20,Fsubject to paying certain bills, such
OL,21,Fas rates.
